                                </div>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <div style="height:50px"></div>
                                    <h4 class="text-white">Sell Service</h4>
                                    <img src="~/img/pro/individual/img-arrow-right.svg" loading="lazy"/>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-center">
                                    <img class="sub-card-inner-ico-1" src="~/img/pro/individual/ico-servicebuyer.svg" loading="lazy"/>
                                    <h4 class="text-secondary">Service Buyer</h4>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-bold text-white text-center">Individual with Individual​</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                                <div class="ml-2 mb-2 p-2 bg-white individual-sub-card-inner-5 justify-content-between">
                                    <div class="d-inline-flex p-2">
                                        <img class="mr-4" style="width:50px;height:50px;" src="~/img/pro/home/freelance-model-1.svg" loading="lazy">
                                        <div>
                                            <div class="text-bold text-primary">Freelance</div>
                                            <div class="text-bold text-primary">(Hourly)</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div style="border-top: 1px solid #7CD8BF">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="p-2">Freelancers are paid based on hourly rate</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12 mb-4">
                                <h3 class="text-bold text-primary text-center">How It Works</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <div class="row h-100">
                                    <div class="col-lg-6 p-5 d-none d-lg-block">
                                        <img class="w-100 hiw-sell-img" src="~/img/pro/individual/howitwork/hiw-sell-1.png" loading="lazy"/>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-lg-6 p-4">
                                        <h4 class="text-bold text-primary mb-4 pb-2" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #7CD8BF">Sell Services</h4>
                                        <img class="w-100 d-lg-none" src="~/img/pro/individual/howitwork/hiw-sell-1.png" loading="lazy"/>
                                        <div class="text-primary text-bold hiw-sell-1">1. Create your service profile</div>
                                        <div class="mb-4 hiw-sell-1">List down your skills & expertise, service model & site, professional fees and availability.</div>
                                        @*<img class="w-100 d-lg-none" src="~/img/pro/individual/howitwork/hiw-sell-2.png" />*@
                                        <div class="text-primary text-bold hiw-sell-2">2. Accept the right service request</div>
                                        <div class="mb-4 hiw-sell-1 hiw-sell-2">Service buyers who wants to hire you will send service request to you. Accept the service request which works best for you. You may also repropose the start date if necessary.</div>
                                        @*<img class="w-100 d-lg-none" src="~/img/pro/individual/howitwork/hiw-sell-3.png" />*@
                                        <div class="text-primary text-bold hiw-sell-1 hiw-sell-3">3. Flexible Engagement</div>
                                        <div class="mb-4 hiw-sell-1 hiw-sell-3">After the deposit of the 1st month professional fees by the service buyer, the service buyer will contact you directly.</div>
                                        @*<img class="w-100 d-lg-none" src="~/img/pro/individual/howitwork/hiw-sell-4.png" />*@
                                        <div class="text-primary text-bold hiw-sell-4">4. Choose your payment preference</div>
                                        <div class="mb-4 hiw-sell-4">
                                            When responding to service request, you may state your payment preference for 2nd month onwards, either to be paid directly by the service buyer or through Yadiyad with Escrow option.<br />
                                            Escrow options enables you to receive timely payment through Yadiyad after completion of service. For more information on Escrow, go to <a class="underline-href" href="/escrow-service-terms">Escrow Service</a>.
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
